      "title": "Benchmarking optimization software with performance profiles",
      "abstract": "We propose performance profiles \u2014 distribution functions for a performance metric \u2014 as a tool for benchmarking and comparing optimization software. We show that performance profiles combine the best features of other tools for performance evaluation."
